org.apache.hadoop.fs.aliyun.oss

Class AliyunOSSFileSystemStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.fs.aliyun.oss.AliyunOSSFileSystemStore

  • public class AliyunOSSFileSystemStore
extends Object
    Core implementation of Aliyun OSS Filesystem for Hadoop. Provides the bridging logic between Hadoop's abstract filesystem and Aliyun OSS.
